window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The tutorial isn’t over yet....</b></p> <p>The system isn’t done with Drake, pushing him and the other participants beyond limits they never knew existed.</p> <p>Killing monsters, surviving ambushes, and leveling up have become routine as Drake fights his way to the tutorial's end.</p> <p>But what awaits beyond the final trial? What kind of world will he step into? And what kind of power will the system grant to those who survive?</p> <p>One thing is certain—there’s no going back.</p> <p>Survive, adapt, and level up once more in this LitRPG Adventure as Drake and his party battle through a deadly landscape that will shape their future.</p>"; 
